            <description><![CDATA[【深圳：800多家社康可直接刷异地医保！<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[666]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/6c/2022_666_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】6月20日上午，深圳市社康中心异地就医直接结算服务启动仪式在福田举行，这也意味着，深圳全市800多家社康中心全部开通异地就医直接结算服务。有个头疼脑热，不必非得去医院，不用再垫付看病钱，不用再来回奔波报销，只需要提前在手机上简单备案，在家门口的社康就能直接刷卡结算。咱就是说，主打一个省时省心省钱。具体怎么操作？能报销多少？戳👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3800%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%B6%E7%A4%BE%E5%BA%B7%E5%8F%AF%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B7%E5%BC%82%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BB%E4%BF%9D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3800%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%B6%E7%A4%BE%E5%BA%B7%E5%8F%AF%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B7%E5%BC%82%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BB%E4%BF%9D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳800多家社康可直接刷异地医保#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfcv2md4w5j20v91uqgtb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfcv2n2zatj20v92ledma.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfcv2litbgj20v91m5wke.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfcv4v5dm0j20wq1sgaj6.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfcv4uoei8j20wr1sy7mp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hfcv2xnc6vj20hs0ey769.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
